# =============================================================================
# Tailwind Editor — Environment Variables
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values:
#   cp .env.example .env
# =============================================================================

# ─── AI Configuration (BYOK) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tailwind Editor uses a Bring Your Own Key (BYOK) model.
# Users provide their own Google Gemini API key in the browser Settings.
# The key is encrypted and stored locally — never sent to any server.
#
# No environment variables are required to run the editor.
